--------
MAC
Label-based
Very granular
Common on RHEL, CentOS, Fedora

AppArmor
---------
MAC
Path-based
Simpler
Common on Ubuntu, Debian

TCP Wrappers
------------
Host-based access control
hosts.allow / hosts.deny
Deprecated

iptables
---------
Kernel firewall
Filters packets
INPUT / OUTPUT / FORWARD chains
